Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.49,0:00:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是第一学期成绩不好的学生\N他们的暑期辅导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.64,0:00:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那么多辅导的学生\N川口也是特别令人你绝望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.05,0:00:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(女教师优香的诱惑教学）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.27,0:00:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不行啊，就我要再补考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么办好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉真差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起，还是来了呢，川口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.24,0:01:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，我很担心能否毕业呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.45,0:01:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在才要努力\N老师会给你特别课程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.52,0:01:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假就返校加油吧\N暑假还返校，感觉很糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.02,0:02:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天川口不但补考还再补考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定对他个别教学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心，你可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口比想象中还差呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.38,0:02:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假完了就又要回到原点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.92,0:02:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为班导，只能打起精神努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:03:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，欢迎回来\N都暑假了还一直工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了班上的学生的将来\N我也得好好努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先给我饭吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公是别校的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间太常错开\N夫妻的感情也就变差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.71,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在没办法，我根本不会念书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚开始啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.66,0:04:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我要个别辅导，超没面子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.26,0:04:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以的，老师挂保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.07,0:04:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然这么没用，身为男人是最差的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.88,0:04:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连女友也没有，整个糟透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着没自信的川口\N整个激发了我的母性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.16,0:04:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让他成为出色的男人\N想让他能拥有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.31,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心，还有空间的，老师会帮你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师谢谢，总觉得平静多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.73,0:05:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先有点成果，就会有自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.74,0:05:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油的话，会有奖励的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖励?什么都可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊，说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，你是男人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.03,0:05:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和老师KISS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.64,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了吧?应该是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.65,0:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊，奖励就真KISS也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.86,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对你要努力拿出成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想都没想就答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.87,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他能用功，也就能接受自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用功就能KISS了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(不知道自己有没有不懂的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(川口君，有在好好用功吗?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（老师，我在复习今天学的微积分)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传讯息了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(好棒呢，川口君就温样加油吧）\N(老师也会为你加油的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有干劲了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.47,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优香，吃东西别用手机啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.15,0:07:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手也是教育，别一直看着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.76,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.96,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.97,0:08:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这是老师该做的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是去年学的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.87,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃，不是和老师约好了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.05,0:09:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想和我KISS吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和川口KISS，老师也要拿出勇气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.34,0:09:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才这么就想放弃了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.88,0:09:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃，不然会原地踏步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么的吗?...对，很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里?..对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.11,0:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以吗?...很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里代入吗?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.14,0:11:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像我要KISS，虽然无法释然\N但川口能努力就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.70,0:11:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊川口，分数一口气成长呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是100分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.91,0:11:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊，短时间能这样就很赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.79,0:11:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.33,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了好，该给你奖励了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口很努力了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.76,0:12:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...要怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸先靠来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的唇好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出来吧...舌头?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.93,0:14:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吸老师的舌头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头品来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.81,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要继续用功，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.83,0:17:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，我会更努力的\N成绩更好的话，还有奖励吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.18,0:17:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没看过女人的身体\N我想看老师的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.73,0:17:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了，那好好用功哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.43,0:18:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话一遇到瓶颈 ，\N就不会放弃努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.11,0:18:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和学生KISS了，而且还在学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.25,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外还做了更深入的约定，为什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.67,0:18:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的指导下成绩成长\N觉得川口这样很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.82,0:18:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是身为老师的罪恶感\N让我的心情动摇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.22,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是老师和学生KISS\N这不允许的事让我兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌，我在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天川口的成绩也更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.94,0:22:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我自己的事一样\N让我感到很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.76,0:22:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师没穿奶罩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.36,0:22:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了让你有干劲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.57,0:22:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是光这么不够?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.19,0:22:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.46,0:23:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为了川口加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.53,0:23:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.47,0:23:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.61,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你能更用功的法术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.61,0:24:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时和川口KISS，\N变得好像理所当然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.28,0:24:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在辅导后，则是沉溺在自慰里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.69,0:24:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口成绩变好\N会想要我作为奖励的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.43,0:24:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份妄想充斥我的脑海里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.66,0:25:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，变这么大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.87,0:25:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是教室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.22,0:25:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.70,0:25:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也来，对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.38,0:26:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.34,0:26:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来用小穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.51,0:27:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.98,0:27:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，这里是教室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.05,0:27:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行在这里插入啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.81,0:27:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来插了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.36,0:27:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.37,0:28:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.25,0:28:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.01,0:28:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.55,0:28:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.18,0:29:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.86,0:29:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.75,0:30:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.67,0:31:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛脱光啊?\N刚回来都是汗，正想洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.29,0:31:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.76,0:31:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，都对呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.97,0:31:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.04,0:31:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要多谢老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.12,0:31:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，难不成在意那约定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.73,0:32:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师别在意，那太大胆\N我也不知道怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.67,0:32:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了努力的目标而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.48,0:32:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口以我为目标而努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.95,0:32:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却...我不能把它当成玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.96,0:32:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好守约才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.96,0:32:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，今天就到这吧，到老师家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.70,0:32:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.30,0:32:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.91,0:32:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞归害羞，就让你看老师的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.99,0:33:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，你是真的想看我的身体?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.33,0:33:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.07,0:33:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要脱光就好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.61,0:33:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，你没问题吗?...我们说好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.49,0:33:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.64,0:33:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦，别那么紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.24,0:33:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都紧张了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.10,0:34:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我脱吧...真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.58,0:34:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没解过，要怎么办?...解开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.78,0:35:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开这里?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.92,0:35:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.13,0:35:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也是...内裤吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.69,0:35:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是为了守约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.70,0:35:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但久违的刺激，让我压抑不了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.11,0:36:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我脱光会害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.92,0:36:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.92,0:36:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何?...老师的奶真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以近点看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.01,0:36:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着哦...真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.96,0:36:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.91,0:37:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里叫阴核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.45,0:37:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这么摸就会好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.40,0:37:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多看点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.07,0:37:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师里头湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.41,0:37:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:46.95,0:37:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.29,0:37:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.10,0:38:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.77,0:38:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.58,0:38:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是插入处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.32,0:38:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里插入吗?.. .插进来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.32,0:38:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.33,0:38:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师里头如何?.. .好热呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.60,0:38:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.34,0:38:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有声音呢...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.88,0:38:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老这么动会很爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.70,0:39:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.14,0:39:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只老师脱光很害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.88,0:39:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口也脱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.35,0:40:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要吗?不用了， 会害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.22,0:40:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱了吧...真的要脱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.69,0:40:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有老师脱会害羞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.10,0:40:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要脱吗?...对，全脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.46,0:40:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:44.60,0:40:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤也要?...对，全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.88,0:41:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.96,0:41:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手不能遮吗?...对，让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.90,0:41:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.91,0:41:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，我兴奋了..害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.72,0:41:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里变好爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.79,0:41:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.87,0:42:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来KISS吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:03.21,0:42:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有教过你怎么亲了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.29,0:42:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.92,0:42:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.13,0:42:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.20,0:43:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么吗?...对，多舔一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.14,0:43:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，这么吗?...对，舌头多动点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.55,0:43:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.69,0:43:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...老师的奶真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:32.50,0:43:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.90,0:43:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多舔一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:45.58,0:43:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:57.05,0:44:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也来舔这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.87,0:44:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔阴核，好爽...这么?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.87,0:44:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:28.82,0:44:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.56,0:44:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:45.24,0:44:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，这么吗?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:55.38,0:44:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.79,0:45:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:16.73,0:45:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.68,0:45:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:33.55,0:45:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.15,0:45:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，不行，那里很脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:43.96,0:45:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给老师吧...不行啦，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:49.17,0:45:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:52.37,0:45:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里很脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.44,0:45:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但好爽的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.58,0:46:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.72,0:46:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.29,0:46:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.83,0:47:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:35.47,0:48:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:15.51,0:49:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，不行，会射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:25.78,0:49:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.45,0:49:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:34.86,0:49:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:41.40,0:49:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插进来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:55.15,0:49:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:06.89,0:50:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.43,0:50:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呢，川口...老师里头好热啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:22.64,0:50:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?...实在好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.05,0:50:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口的老二也好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:52.80,0:50:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:03.21,0:51:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.35,0:51:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.44,0:51:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原好深好爽...我也好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.86,0:51:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好湿热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:55.13,0:51:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:01.27,0:52:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:09.68,0:52:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口好赞...老师也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:21.56,0:52:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来，多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:50.39,0:52:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...这么来用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:58.93,0:53:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.47,0:53:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:28.16,0:53:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，可以舔奶吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:33.10,0:53:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来多用点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:40.04,0:53:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:46.58,0:53:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多用点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:50.58,0:53:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来插深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:57.92,0:54:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真行，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:10.20,0:54:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:13.67,0:54:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是做爱吗?...对，这就是做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:19.28,0:54:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是女人的那里?...对，多动一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.55,0:54:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这么爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:42.23,0:54:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:04.79,0:55:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:10.13,0:55:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:16.00,0:55:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里?...对，这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:22.14,0:55:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪?...就这个洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.88,0:55:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来插入咯...再来一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.42,0:55:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了...腰动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:43.76,0:55:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么?...就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:48.43,0:55:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我插到老师里头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:56.17,0:56:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那里多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:00.44,0:56:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口真行...老师， 可以摸奶吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:07.52,0:56:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，多用点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:35.15,0:56:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，顶到了，真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.69,0:56:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子吗?...对，多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:59.84,0:57:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口，真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.04,0:57:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:10.11,0:57:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真行，多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:19.06,0:57:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，好爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:29.20,0:57:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:33.34,0:57:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:54.29,0:57:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里头在动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:06.44,0:58:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:09.64,0:58:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.98,0:58:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:24.72,0:58:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全射出来吧...可以射吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:31.80,0:58:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.21,0:59:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，你太性感了，没办法专心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:00.42,1:00:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经能用功了\N接下来要练你的集中力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:10.96,1:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意老师，好好专心用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.26,1:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.06,1:00:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了，专心用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:50.73,1:00:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是锻练，不管怎么都要专心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:02.08,1:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:14.76,1:01:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志，有专心吗?...有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:23.57,1:01:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有专心啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.30,1:01:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过老二变很大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:32.78,1:01:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然变大了，但我还是在专心用功啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:40.38,1:01:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:49.86,1:01:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有专心吗?...有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.80,1:02:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好专心用功...老师，我可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.34,1:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.75,1:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有好好专心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:31.24,1:02:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好专心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.51,1:02:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:46.05,1:02:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:02.20,1:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.94,1:03:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以试一下吗?..老师，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:37.43,1:03:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:03.19,1:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:11.20,1:04:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.25,1:05:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.62,1:05:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:47.22,1:06:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，受不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:55.77,1:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么用会射的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.60,1:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，这么激烈会射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:23.04,1:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.95,1:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志，在补习吗?暑假都过一半了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.89,1:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，让他看书也是浪费时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:17.23,1:11:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:18.83,1:11:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是很努力的，别瞧不起人出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:29.11,1:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志，很有男子气概，很帅哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:35.65,1:11:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，突然就一头热
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.65,1:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成绩也变好了，觉得一切都不错了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:48.06,1:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏老师我才能有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:55.00,1:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很危险呢\N要是被看到在含就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:00.47,1:12:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啦，这里可是教室呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:05.14,1:12:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人来就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.95,1:12:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10分后到体育仓库来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:54.39,1:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，做什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:25.62,1:13:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.29,1:13:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚广志实在很帅呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:38.57,1:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师不是有给你奖励?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:44.18,1:13:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次换你给老饰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:52.72,1:13:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要什么?...像大人一样渴求我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:01.66,1:14:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:05.13,1:14:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.33,1:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:16.74,1:14:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:27.55,1:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:20.27,1:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:08.45,1:16:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:23.67,1:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:40.62,1:16:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志，变厉害了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:46.09,1:16:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，老师想玩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:16.39,1:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裤子脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:41.35,1:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:53.36,1:17:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，变好硬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:30.86,1:18:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:47.55,1:18:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:51.42,1:18:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的屁股好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:02.49,1:19:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下吧...躺着吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:25.32,1:19:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感吗?...好爽，蛋也用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:56.95,1:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:01.89,1:20:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:14.57,1:20:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.06,1:20:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，可以坐上来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.40,1:20:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我坐上去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:15.03,1:21:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么吗?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:27.71,1:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:43.32,1:21:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.08,1:23:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:45.04,1:23:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:59.06,1:24:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:09.07,1:24:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:21.61,1:24:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:48.44,1:24:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:03.39,1:25:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了啊，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:12.46,1:25:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了，可以射吗?老师...射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:19.14,1:25:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:29.41,1:25:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:34.62,1:25:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.83,1:25:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:10.25,1:26:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然年轻呢，明明刚刚才一发的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:16.39,1:26:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，这点我也有自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:23.20,1:26:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:36.01,1:26:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和学生的秘密关系\N虽然明白那是不允许的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:42.69,1:26:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却愈陷愈深
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:25.40,1:27:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，欢迎回来...你好像很开心啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:31.80,1:27:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:34.21,1:27:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做了什么吗?...才没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:43.95,1:27:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在暑假要结束时\N广志的成绩变得很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:51.69,1:27:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在班上也排得到前头了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:55.16,1:28:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志，真的很努力呢\N一个暑假就进步那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:02.23,1:28:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏老师了，要是没老师在\N我一定一直是个垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:21.99,1:28:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不用补习了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:26.52,1:28:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，不给我奖励吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:32.53,1:28:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和老师在这里搞...在学校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:37.60,1:28:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不要，我就在这强奸老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:41.47,1:28:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么强硬了啊，明明才破处没多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:24.11,1:30:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:32.52,1:30:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:37.05,1:30:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了呢，老师奋教室一样下流呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:53.74,1:30:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师怎么变这么热?...广志好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:53.93,1:31:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都流汗了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:00.87,1:32:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的腋下味道也很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:06.21,1:32:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师舌头出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:49.19,1:32:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:53.72,1:32:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:59.06,1:33:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:02.53,1:33:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:06.80,1:33:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真赞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:10.27,1:33:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈来愈湿呢...广志，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:16.28,1:33:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:21.49,1:33:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师爽吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:03.26,1:34:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊?老师，这里吗?....就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:16.87,1:34:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道老师在爽了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:23.15,1:34:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:44.24,1:34:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:48.64,1:34:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翘好吧，朝这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:58.12,1:35:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:06.79,1:35:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤都勒住了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:22.01,1:35:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最爱老师的屁股了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:29.21,1:35:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啦...爽吗?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:00.04,1:36:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直抖，真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:03.11,1:36:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:36.08,1:36:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:44.76,1:36:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...是吗?脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:51.83,1:36:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教室看老师的小穴呢...害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:02.51,1:37:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，全用开了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:10.11,1:37:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吗?...害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:16.25,1:37:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老师流出黏滑的汁了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:23.06,1:37:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:27.60,1:37:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...是吗?那就来更爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:04.70,1:38:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...这么?....好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:15.78,1:38:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:19.65,1:38:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都牵丝了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:23.65,1:38:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你看，都这么了.可以多舔吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:32.33,1:38:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来多舔一点吧，好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:39.14,1:38:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:56.35,1:38:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:04.23,1:39:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:20.38,1:39:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:48.54,1:39:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...看这里，超多汁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:57.08,1:40:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音响遍教室呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:02.69,1:40:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，不觉得害羞吗?...害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:10.96,1:40:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:18.04,1:40:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊...不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:27.91,1:40:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:33.25,1:40:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:38.32,1:40:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师湿答答啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:57.01,1:40:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:11.56,1:41:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了，舔我奶头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:33.31,1:41:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:40.52,1:41:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:46.79,1:41:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来互舔嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:50.53,1:41:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想舔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:17.49,1:42:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这么用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:37.78,1:42:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，再多一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:46.58,1:42:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的嘴真爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:00.73,1:43:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来互舔嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:07.67,1:43:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:46.17,1:44:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:51.91,1:44:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:35.95,1:45:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:40.49,1:45:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:49.97,1:45:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:55.17,1:45:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来好多汁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:09.19,1:46:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:18.40,1:46:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，到讲台翘好屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:32.41,1:46:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋呢，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:38.28,1:46:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来...想要插啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:43.35,1:46:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要被插啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:54.57,1:46:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:12.05,1:47:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:34.34,1:47:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:39.14,1:47:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流汁了呢...不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:52.62,1:47:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:56.23,1:47:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:00.50,1:48:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可以吗?有点难呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:09.44,1:48:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在平时上课的地方，和老师搞起来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:28.93,1:48:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:36.27,1:48:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:00.02,1:49:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:10.97,1:49:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:26.98,1:49:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚上来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:33.66,1:49:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又全开了，从后面来，连屁眼都看光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.58,1:50:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:58.81,1:51:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:02.15,1:51:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:16.69,1:51:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:19.90,1:51:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:28.57,1:51:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:38.85,1:51:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:49.53,1:51:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:09.41,1:52:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:48.79,1:52:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么如何?...好赞，都插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:55.59,1:53:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊，在教室插如何啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:07.61,1:53:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教室里做如何?...实在是好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:27.76,1:53:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:34.70,1:53:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:47.24,1:53:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:56.59,1:53:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:15.01,1:54:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:52.11,1:54:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:57.45,1:54:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:03.99,1:55:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:12.53,1:55:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:22.67,1:55:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在抖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:31.48,1:55:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:37.09,1:55:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:45.10,1:55:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:49.23,1:55:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊?...小穴好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:01.38,1:56:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:17.26,1:56:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞...我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:22.87,1:56:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射老师的脸吗?...全射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:35.01,1:56:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:41.55,1:56:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:20.12,1:57:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只读书，连做爱也进步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:25.60,1:57:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教的东西，广志都学起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:33.74,1:57:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2学期起，就没机会2个人一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:40.01,1:57:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也代表着没办法和广志做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:45.62,1:57:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的身体己经受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:53.09,1:57:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:00.97,1:58:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:04.17,1:58:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和广志的秘密关系，后来也持续着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:10.44,1:58:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广志好像变了个人一样，\N成长为一个坚强的男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:18.58,1:58:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个腰动得让我去个不停...
